Forge 1~
 
 
 
  As you enter Forge's sacred alter you immediately fall to your knees and
  hope Forge isn't angry at you for violating his holy sanctuary with your
  putrid and vile presence.  You crawl before his enormous statue and say
  "What is thy bidding my master?"  The statue begins to glow with the his
  power, releasing a massive bolt of red energy which sends you flying to 
  the back wall.  When you regain consciousness, you find your extremely
  strong and lusting for blood.  Once Forge had put his black mark on your
  soul you realize you are his eternal slave and a happy at being so.
 
~
