sign~
 
 
 
 Hello, this is my room. If you are here as a friend, thanks for gracing
 it's presence :) While you are here kick back, relax, have some fun, take
 a snooze. But if you pop my bed, I'm going to use you to fill it back up.
 
 If you are not here as a friend, go ahead and kick back and relax a while 
 too, I'll be here soon, and I've been needing some more people to...help 
 me gain the favor of the almighty Forge and Rygar..
 
                                   Bielnack, General of Hell
 
~
