Brandy~
 
 
 
  You walk into a bar.  Here you'll find the finest Brandy in land.  When
  you look behind the bar, you see a sign the reads:  Have a  seat and 
  unwind!  We all deserve a shot after a long day of slaying zoning the 
  hardest parts of the MUD.  You fell at ease knowing Brandy is somehow
  always looking after you.
 
~
E
Bielnack~
 
 
 
  Glancing around, the room seems quite plain...for a Hell-Spawn. There are 
  two altars on one side of the room, awaiting the daily sacrifices of 
  enemy flesh to Forge and Rygar. On the opposite side of the room there
  is a large oddly colored ornate waterbed. Approaching the waterbed, you
  begin to realize why the room smells so bad...It seems that the bed 
  itself is filled with the blood and eyeballs of the occupant's slain foe.
  How nice...Upon the wall rest a Group portrait of some of HELL's elite 
  members. Next to it hangs a long silver framed piece of parchment. 
  Examining the parchment you see it is a list of rival clan members who 
  have fallen to the iron fist of HELL. There seems to be plenty of room at
  the end for more names. A sign seems to be hovering above the waterbed...
  ...hmm.
 
~
