Laya~
 
 
 
  When you enter Laya's Bondage Chamber your mind becomes soft like jello
  and you have a sudden will to submit. You are amazed at all the leather
  ..on the couch, on the bed, in her closet, and well just about everywhere.
  You now know why it's a bondage chamber as you see a broken down bed, and
  not from age. The black sheets and shackles give you a provoking insight 
  into Laya's more specialized interests. Now you just want to sit around
  and wait for Laya to return to practice a little BONDAGE!!!
 
~
E
Rygar~
 
 
 
  As you step through the arched door you feel a powerful force surround 
  you.  You know that Rygar, the Almighty, COMM of HELL, would be watching
  you.  You lay the fresh corpses of your victims into the large pair of
  outstretched hands floating here. Then realize a minor thousand kills is
  not enough to truly honor Rygar. You desperately beg him to spare you
  meager life.  Suddenly a strange sensation flows through and you hear the
  word more and understand.    
 
~
