Slaverlord~
 
 
 
  When you enter Slaverlord's Dungeon you hear the screams of some terrified
  mindless slaves hiding in the shadows.  Their wailing begins to cease when
  they realize you are not going to beat them with a spiked whip like
  Slaverlord traditionally does.  You notice a pool of blood near the large
  altar to Forge and you know a  sacrifice had recently taken place...and 
  you don't want to be next.
 
~
